                        G A M E    N O T E S


      Foosball - Street Edition is a 5 VS 5 arcade football
      game, that puts you in control of 9 teams of foosball
      players, each one with unique skills and abilities. Far
      from trying to imitate a football simulation like other
      games, Foosball - Street Edition focus in offering new
      game modes that take the player to a brand new and fresh
      approach into football. You have never played Bread &
      Cheese, Score to Win, Pass to Ten or any of the others.
      Are you ready?


                       G R O U P    N O T E S
